		Though, as my interest grew, I delved into pursing photography as deeper passion and artform. 
		This brought forth my transition into using an actual camera body to take my photos.
		I've gravitated towards the brand 'Nikon'.

	Listed here is a ranked table of my favorite cameras and a description of how I used them.

